<section class="landscape-demo" aria-label="风景与夜景层次示意图">
  <div class="landscape-demo__grid">
    <div class="landscape-demo__card">
      <div class="landscape-demo__badge">风景看层次</div>
      <div class="landscape-demo__scene landscape-demo__scene--layers">
        <div class="landscape-demo__front">前景</div>
        <div class="landscape-demo__mid">中景</div>
        <div class="landscape-demo__back">远景</div>
      </div>
      <p>风景一旦只有天空和地面，照片很容易空。前景、中景、远景一旦分清，画面马上会更完整。</p>
    </div>
    <div class="landscape-demo__card">
      <div class="landscape-demo__badge">夜景看主光源</div>
      <div class="landscape-demo__scene landscape-demo__scene--night">
        <div class="landscape-demo__glow landscape-demo__glow--main"></div>
        <div class="landscape-demo__road"></div>
        <div class="landscape-demo__glow landscape-demo__glow--small"></div>
        <div class="landscape-demo__tag">先找最主要的光</div>
      </div>
      <p>夜景不是越亮越好，先找到主要光源，再决定怎么围绕它组织建筑、道路和人物，画面会干净很多。</p>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

